<h3>Outer Table</h3><p>The Outer Table is the name given to the table that contains your entire website.</p>
<p><strong>Position </strong>- Choose how you want your website to be aligned in the browser (if less that 100% width). </p>
<p><strong>Width</strong> - Choose either px or % (include the symbol or it will not work correctly.&nbsp; Many website are 800px wide or 100%.</p>
<p><strong>Border </strong>- You choose to put a border our your website.&nbsp; Choose the width of the border.</p>
<p><strong>Border Color </strong>- Choose the border color that will surround your website.&nbsp; Only applies if you have specified a border width of 1px or greater.</p>




